[src:scim-provisioning/provisioning-technology] During the provisioning, the service mediation device translates the service and the corresponding parameters of the service to one or more services/parameters on the network elements involved.
[src:scim-provisioning/provisioning-technology] The algorithm used to translate a system service into network services is called **provisioning logic**.
